### Component 4: Web Frontend
A beautiful, highly accessible single-page application under `frontend/` matching the **Minimal Single Column** pattern and the **Accessible & Ethical** style.
Colors: Primary `#0891B2`, Secondary `#22D3EE`, CTA `#059669`, Background `#ECFEFF`, Text `#164E63`.
Features:
- Micro-interactions (smooth transitions on button hover, pulsing recording state).
- MediaRecorder API to record audio in real-time.
- Visual wave or recording status indicator.
- Fetch API to POST the audio to the Django backend.
- Accessibility features (keyboard focus outline, aria-labels, WCAG contrast).

